fields.calculatedFormula:
IF(
    ISBLANK(Birthdate),
    
    '',

    IF(
        And(
            Month(Today()) >= Month(Birthdate),
            Day(Today()) >=  Day(Birthdate)
        ),

        TEXT(Year(Today())- Year(Birthdate)) & " " & "years" & " " & TEXT(Month(Today())-Month(Birthdate)) & " " & "months" & " " & TEXT(Day(Today())-Day(Birthdate)),
    
        IF(
            And(month(Today())< month(Birthdate), Day(Today())>= Day(Birthdate)),
        
            TEXT(Year(Today())-Year(Birthdate)-1) & " " & "years" & " " & TEXT(12 - Month(Birthdate)+month(Today())) & " " & "months" & " " & TEXT(Day(Today())-Day(Birthdate)),
    
            if(
                And( month(Today())< month(Birthdate), Day(Today())< Day(Birthdate)),

                (TEXT( (Year(Today())-Year(Birthdate)-1)) & " " & "years" & " " & TEXT((12 - Month(Birthdate)+month(Today())-1)) & " " & "months" ) & " " &
                    CASE(month(Birthdate),
                        2, TEXT( (28 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        4, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        6, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        9, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        11, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        TEXT( (31 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today()))
                    ),
                if(
                    And( month(Today())= month(Birthdate), Day(Today())< Day(Birthdate)),
                
                    (TEXT(Year(Today())- Year(Birthdate)-1)) & " " & "years" & " " & "11" & " " & "months" & " " &
                    CASE(month(Birthdate),
                        2, TEXT( (28 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        4, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        6, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        9, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        11, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        TEXT( (31 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today()))
                    ),
                    (TEXT(Year(Today())- Year(Birthdate))) & " " & "years" & " " & TEXT(Month(Today())-Month(Birthdate)-1) & " " & "months" & " " &
                    CASE(month(Birthdate),
                        2, TEXT( (28 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        4, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        6, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        9, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        11, TEXT( (30 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today())),
                        TEXT( (31 - Day(Birthdate))+ Day(Today()))
                    )
                )
            )
        )
    ) & " " & "days"
)
